creator: Indi.com
descriptionHtml:
What do your friends look to you as the expert in? Have a unique skill? It’s time to be rewarded for your individuality.

indi enables you to make money for being yourself. With multiple different revenue earning features available, it’s easy to start getting paid for your expertise and influence. indi makes it fun and exciting to turn your passion and skills into a business - you’ll be surprised to see how you can cash in on your passions.

An Easy Way to Make Money:

Tag Products with “things I love”
Do friends and followers think you rock at something specific? Awesome! Fashion, beauty, sports, art, accessories, home decor, travel plans - you name it - just tag ‘things I love’ products in your social content and make a commission every time somebody buys from your indi link. You can even copy & message your friends a “things i love” product link for a more personal recommendation via any messaging platform...Let’s be real, you deserve to earn a little cash when your friends follow your lead.

More about “things i love”
indi helps you earn commission every time somebody uses one of your tagged product links to buy from a retailer. With 70 MILLION products and all of your favorite retailers, it’s super easy to share the things you love with your audience and make recommendations based on your personal knowledge and style.

By working with more than 1,700 retailers, indi covers: fashion, fitness, home decor, apparel, sports, accessories, concerts & live events, athletic wear, travel, outdoor activities, fitness, art, music, education, and more!

Sharing is super easy. Just find a product you like (or have), link it to your content (something you created or you can use the product shot from the retailer), and share with your friends and followers.

indi seamlessly links content to Instagram, Facebook, Youtube, whatsapp, email, text/sms, and more. No matter how you stay connected with your network, indi lets you share with them with just a few taps - making it easy to share your influence and get paid.

Being an entrepreneur in the modern gig economy
indi’s revenue earning tools blend together your social media content sharing habits and individuals skills & specialties, allowing you to be an entrepreneur in the modern gig economy. indi is an easy and convenient way to turn your passion into a business and earn revenue as an entrepreneur, whether it’s a side hustle gig & extra way to earn cash or you turn your expertise & influence into a full-time dream job.. If you already have a business related to your skills and expertise, indi provides plenty of additional revenue streams to maximize your sales and business growth. Maximize your potential revenue and social audience with indi - cash in on your passion.

title: Indi - Cash In on your Passion

creator: Indi.com
descriptionHtml:
Indi is a tool that empowers you to make money from your social media connections. With multiple different revenue features, it’s easy to start getting paid for your expertise and influence. Indi makes it fun & exciting to turn your passion and skills into a business, side-hustle, or hobby. You’ll be surprised to see how many ways you can cash in on your passions.

5 Easy Ways to Make Money:

Tag Products with “Love it”
Fashion, beauty, sports, art, accessories, home decor, travel plans - you name it - just tag products in your content using the Indi tool before sharing on social and then make a commission every time somebody buys from your Indi link! You can even send your friends a personal recommendation via any messaging platform.

Teach & share your skills with “Know it”
Are you an expert in a particular field? Heck yeah you are. Your expertise is valuable, no matter what unique field you’re a master of! From interior decorating to sports drills, music lessons to art classes, and everything in between... Share your knowledge with “Know it.” Create on-demand videos to share your expertise with your followers, set your price, and get paid per viewer. Plus - you can still tag products to recommend and earn commission in your on-demand content!

Give personal advice or reviews with “Check it”
Do people often ask your opinion on a certain topic? Of course they do. “Check it” allows you to have custom, personal two-way recorded videos with individual followers to help them get custom feedback. Tips, lessons, advice, reviewing ideas or content - “Check it” gives you the opportunity to get rewarded while developing a personal relationship with your audience.

Brighten somebody’s day with “Shout it”
Do people admire you for something unique? Obviously! Then share the love and make a fan’s day by giving them personalized content. Celebrate and participate in your audiences important personal moments. All you have to do is 1) set your price, 2) let your audience know you're available for personalized content, 3) share your Indi profile, and 4) respond to your audiences content requests.

Indi Referral Program
We're all about helping you make money... so we've made it super easy to get started. We give a $20 bonus plus 12-months commission for each qualified referral!

More about tagging products:
Earn commission every time somebody uses one of your tagged product links to buy from a retailer. With over 80 MILLION products and all of your favorite retailers, it’s easy to share the things you love with your audience & make recommendations based on your personal knowledge and style.

With almost 2,000 retailers, Indi covers: fashion, fitness, home decor, apparel, sports, accessories, concerts & live events, athletic wear, travel, outdoor activities, fitness, arts, music, education, and more!

Sharing is easy. Just find a product you like (or have), tag it to your content, and share with your friends and followers. You can even use the retailers product image instead of your own content.

Indi seamlessly links your content to Instagram, Facebook, Youtube, whatsapp, email, text/sms, and more. No matter how you stay connected with your network, Indi lets you share with them in just a few taps - making it easy to share & get paid!

Being an entrepreneur:
Indi’s revenue earning tools blend your social media content sharing habits and your individual skills & specialties, allowing you to be an entrepreneur in the gig economy. Indi is a convenient way to turn your passion into a business and earn revenue as an entrepreneur, whether it’s a side hustle gig & extra way to earn cash or you're able to turn your expertise & influence into a full-time dream job. If you already have your own business (ex: fitness instructor, influencer, stylist, blogger, etc.), Indi can provide additional revenue streams to maximize sales and business growth. Maximize your potential revenue & social audience with Indi - cash in on your passion.
